org.deeplearning4j.graph.iterator

Interface GraphWalkIterator<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomWalkIterator, WeightedRandomWalkIterator

    public interface GraphWalkIterator<T>
    Interface/iterator representing a sequence of walks on a graph For example, a GraphWalkIterator<T> can represesnt a set of independent random walks on a graph
